### Welcome to TJTeru's GitHub Pages.

My name is Roger Meike.  I am a researcher and entrepreneur who has worked at several major research organizations and start up companies in Silicon Valley and beyond.  However, I have created this persona for my personal work.  This work is for fun hobbies and the plethora of projects that never get enough time.

![Me](http://yoroger.com/images/RogerBanner.jpg)
